The '''''Duergo''''' was [[Race Kartan]]'s personal [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighter]]. A battle occurred between Kartan and [[Jango Fett/Legends|Jango Fett]] where many vessels were destroyed, including three [[Lupus-class missile frigate|Missile Frigates]] and numerous mercenary starfighters. During the course of the battle, Fett disabled the ''Duergo'' to collect the [[Bounty/Legends|bounty]] on Kartan.

{{Ship-stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
The ''Duergo'' appears as the primary target in the Jango Fett bonus mission of ''[[Star Wars: Jedi Starfighter]]''. This ship has the same 3D model as the [[Unidentified mercenary craft]] from [[Star Wars: Starfighter (video game)|''Star Wars: Starfighter'']].

